---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 1, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — IData"
  description="How IData Corporation collects, uses, and protects the personal information you share with us."
>
  <Nav />
  <PageHeader
    headline="Privacy Policy"
    subheadline={`Last updated ${lastUpdated}`}
  />

  <section class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content animate-on-scroll">
        <p>
          IData Corporation ("IData," "we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy
          explains what information we collect when you visit <a href="https://idata.net">idata.net</a>
          (the "Site") or contact us, how we use that information, and the choices you have. By using the
          Site, you agree to the practices described here.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information in two ways:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Information you provide.</strong> When you complete our contact form, we collect the
            details you submit — such as your name, company, email address, phone number, the topic you
            select, and any message you send. You choose what to share; the name, company, email, and topic
            fields are required to submit the form.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> Like most websites, our hosting and
            service providers may automatically record basic technical data such as your IP address,
            browser type, device information, and the pages you view. This information helps us keep the
            Site secure and understand how it is used.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and communicate with you about our services;</li>
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the Site and our offerings;</li>
          <li>Protect the security and integrity of the Site; and</li>
          <li>Comply with our legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not sell or rent your personal information, and we do not use the details you submit for
          advertising.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We rely on a small number of trusted third-party services to operate the Site. These providers
          process data on our behalf and are subject to their own privacy policies:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Formspree</strong> processes submissions from our contact form and delivers them to us
            by email.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Fonts</strong> serves the typefaces used on the Site, which may involve your
            browser requesting font files from Google's servers.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          The Site does not use cookies to track you or to serve advertising. Any cookies set are limited
          to those strictly necessary for the Site and its service providers to function.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain the information you submit through the contact form for as long as needed to respond to
          your inquiry and maintain our business records, after which we delete or anonymize it unless a
          longer retention period is required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Choices and Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on where you live, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete the personal
          information we hold about you, or to object to certain processing. To exercise any of these
          rights, contact us using the details below and we will respond in accordance with applicable law.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your information. However, no
          method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we
          cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          The Site is intended for businesses and professionals and is not directed to children under the
          age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated"
          date above. Your continued use of the Site after any change indicates your acceptance of the
          updated policy.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please reach out
          to us at <a href="mailto:info@idata.net">info@idata.net</a> or through our
          <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: 80px 0 120px;
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 740px;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    padding-left: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .legal-content li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .legal-content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
